## Accelerator Cable Installation Note  


- Carry out the "ACCELERATOR CABLE INSPECTION/ADJUSTMENT" procedure after installing the accelerator cable.  


## ACCELERATOR CABLE INSPECTION/ADJUSTMENT  


1. Verify that the throttle valve is at the closed throttle position. 
2. Measure the free play of the accelerator cable.  


Free play 1- 3 mm {0.04- 0.11 in}  


3. If not within the specification, adjust by turning locknuts A.  


Tightening torque 9.8- 14 N·m {1.0- 1.5 kgf·m, 7.3- 10 ft·lbf}  

